# Git commit qoidalari

Commit yaratganda quyidagilarga rioya qil:

- Xabar **o'zbek tilida**, **qisqa** (1 qator, ~50 belgigacha) va **aniq** bo'lsin
- Nima o'zgarganini tushuntirsin: `fix`, `add`, `update` o'rniga to'g'ridan-to'g'ri vazifani yoz
- Inglizcha commit xabarlaridan foydalanma
- **`Co-authored-by` qo'shma** — hech qachon `Co-authored-by: Cursor` yoki boshqa co-author satrlarini qo'shma

## Namunalar

```
Admin panelga xodim qidiruv qo'shildi
Vazifa statusi yangilash xatosi tuzatildi
Android login ekrani dizayni yangilandi
Backend JWT muddati sozlandi
.gitignore va docker-compose qo'shildi
```

## Noto'g'ri

```
Fix bug in task module
Initial commit: Vazifa task management system
Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>
```
